schools.name: Boerne - Samuel V Champion High School

data.description: Highly desirable one-story 4 bed/2 bath,  2132 sqft home on cul-de-sac in Fair Oaks Ranch! Open floor plan features spacious living room w/charming wood-burning fireplace & high ceilings, recent renovations include beautiful dark wood floors and granite throughout.  Large windows allow for plenty of natural light. Extra large, private backyard w/mature trees and covered patio is the perfect entertaining space! Excellent Boerne ISD schools including FOR Elementary within walking distance.   WELCOME HOME!
data.whatILove:
Not only a great location as it is on a cul-de-sac with very little traffic, you can easily walk to the club, pool, golf course, elementary school or within a couple of minutes be on your way at highway speeds to IH-10 and San Antonio.

Probably one of the best things about this home to me is the covered back porch that faces the East meaning that you can enjoy the rising of the Sun in the morning while sipping your breakfast beverage and your evening beverage of choice while in the shade and enjoying the serene view.  In addition to that, you can easily place 4 tables of 4 with lots of maneuvering room on this porch making it an excellent place to entertain.
